text: Raiza Goulão (born February 28, 1991) is a Brazilian cross-country cyclist. She placed 20th in the women's cross-country race at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian female cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Brazil Category:Cyclists at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 2015 Pan American Games Category:South American Games silver medalists for Brazil Category:South American Games medalists in cycling Category:Competitors at the 2014 South American Games
